WEBVTT

00:00.526 --> 00:06.819
Use "a" before consonant sounds and "an" before vowel sounds.

00:13.273 --> 00:15.329
He has a car.

00:18.826 --> 00:21.253
She is a woman.

00:24.846 --> 00:26.839
They have a banana.

00:30.675 --> 00:33.041
A mouse is eating.

00:36.744 --> 00:39.047
She is wearing a hat.

00:43.158 --> 00:45.398
This is a flower.

00:49.577 --> 00:52.313
He is eating an apple.

00:55.524 --> 00:57.663
This is an airplane.

01:02.036 --> 01:04.339
Bring an umbrella if it rains.

01:08.285 --> 01:10.960
This is an insect.

01:14.366 --> 01:16.917
He is an old man.

01:20.260 --> 01:22.997
A dog is an animal.

